## 12. Architecture Verification ✅

| Requirement | Status |
|---|---|
| Log ingestion via HTTP | ✅ `POST /api/ingest` |
| Prompt firewall (sanitization before AI) | ✅ Regex + DB policies |
| AI-powered analysis | ✅ Gemini 2.5 Flash with structured JSON output |
| Event-driven architecture | ✅ 7 Kafka topics |
| traceId propagation | ✅ Through every event |
| Duplicate detection | ✅ Via `tempId` |
| Conditional alerting | ✅ confidence > 0.7 + high/critical |
| Audit trail | ✅ `audit_logs`, `system_events`, `policy_logs` |
| Notifications | ✅ Slack + Email via Resend |
| Auth & rate limiting | ✅ JWT + Redis rate limiter |
| Caching | ✅ Redis with X-Cache headers |
| Health checks | ✅ All services have `/health` |
| Docker deployment | ✅ docker-compose.yml |

**The backend architecture is complete.** Next step is choosing between building the dashboard or the SDK first.
